<expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅr gnade vnd guten
                            <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> . fürter <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_470_r1l16"><expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ʒu
                                <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> nach <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
