                                <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_470_r1l18"><expan cert="unknown">H</expan>  von vvölfelſtorffs
                        vnd Nıkel vörſters <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . tun wır
